==English==
===Noun===
'''clitic''' ([[clitics]])

# (''linguistics'') a [[morpheme]] that functions like a word, but appears not as an independent [[word]] but rather is always attached to a following or preceding word. In English, the [[possessive]] ''[[-'s]]'' is an example.

